node.text: Having Covid & Influenza at the same time for 3 weeks WAS HORRIBLE. I literally felt helpless, so sick & I lost 8 pounds being sick.😞But lesson learned - no more attending big get togethers. I’m just happy to be healthy & feel my best again!💖 EVEN THO I STILL CANT TASTE MY FOOD AFTER ALMOST A MONTH LOL. God is great & I’m finally back on social media! I MISSED YOU FRIENDS!🥺🧡✨💓

Listening to music just got better.  #teampixel
